<h2 style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:18px; margin:0 0 15px 0;'>
  Hello
  <strong style='color:#2FBF05;'>{{userName}}</strong>,
</h2>

<p
  style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666666; margin:0 0 20px 0;'
>
  Forgot your password? No problem. Here’s the link to create a new one:
</p>

<!-- Centered button -->
<table
  role='presentation'
  border='0'
  cellpadding='0'
  cellspacing='0'
  align='center'
  style='margin:20px auto;'
>
  <tr>
    <td align='center' bgcolor='#4AD31F' style='border-radius:5px;'>
      <a
        href='{{resetUrl}}'
        target='_blank'
        style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; padding:12px 24px; display:inline-block; border-radius:5px; font-weight:bold;'
      >
        Reset my password
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p
  style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#4AD31F; word-break:break-all; margin:0 0 20px 0;'
>
  {{resetUrl}}
</p>

<p
  style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666666; margin:20px 0 10px 0;'
>
  This link will be active for
  {{minutes}}
  minutes. If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this
  message.
</p>

<p
  style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666666; margin:20px 0 10px 0;'
>
  Once you update your password, you’ll be able to log in again and manage your
  assets securely.
</p>

<p
  style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666666; margin:20px 0 10px 0;'
>
  Have questions? We’re here to help.
</p>

<p
  style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666666; margin:20px 0 10px 0;'
>
  Best regards,
  <br />
  The
  <strong style='color:#2FBF05;'>{{appName}}</strong>
  Team
</p>